Niluka Ekanayake bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị na mba Sri Lanka na onye na-agụ gbasara kpakpando

Onye isi ala Maithripala Sirisena họpụtara ya site na 17 Machị 2016 ruo 11 Eprel 2018 dị ka Gọvanọ nke ịrị nke Central Province. A họpụtakwara ya dị ka Gọvanọ nke itoolu nke Sabaragamuwa Province, Sri Lanka site na 12 Eprel 2018 ruo 31 Disemba 2018. Na Jenụwarị 2019 a họpụtara ya dị ka Onye isi oche nke State Timber Corporation (STC).
Ọ bụ onye LGBT mbụ na nwanyị transgender mbụ nwere ọfịs Gọvanọ na mpaghara Sri Lanka, a na-ewerekwa ya dị ka onye isi transgender mbụ nke gọọmentị n'ụwa.
